column631: I was asked to determine the stereotypically of Asians; if no group was specified, I chose based on minorities as a whole

column632: some of my contradictory responses were bc people (generally, in places like where we live) are friendly, but antisocial.
If you decide to give me credit for participating in this study, I would appreciate if you made your decision before June 5th. In any case, thank you for allowing me to participate in your study.
This study really made me rethink how I see my family, friends and fellow members of the Asian American Pacific Islander community. Appreciate the opportunity! Take care and be safe!
